as you carve and then polish.&rsquo; - The meaning is the same, I apprehend, as that which you have just expressed.&rdquo; The Master said, &ldquo;With one like Ci, I can begin to talk about the odes. I told him one point, and he knew its proper sequence.&rdquo;
